<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>Портфолио | ALBE DIGITAL — проекты и кейсы</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Портфолио ALBE digital — реальные проекты для банков, e-commerce, фитнес-студий. Кейсы, результаты, технологии. Заказать разработку сайта.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="портфолио разработки сайтов, кейсы, примеры работ, albe digital">
    <meta name="author" content="Albe Digital">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://albe.su/portfolio/">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Портфолио | ALBE DIGITAL — проекты и кейсы">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Реальные проекты ALBE digital. Банки, e-commerce, фитнес-приложения. Результаты и технологии.">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://albe.su/portfolio/">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0D1117">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 40 40'%3E%3Crect width='40' height='40' fill='%23F5B700'/%3E%3Ctext x='20' y='28' font-size='24' text-anchor='middle' fill='black' font-weight='500'%3EA%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zen+Dots&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #0D1117; color: #E6EDF5; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400; }
        body::before { content: ""; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.65' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E"); background-repeat: repeat; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1; }
        .container { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
        h1 { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #FFFFFF; }
        h2 { font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 500; position: relative; display: inline-block; }
        h2::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -12px; left: 0; width: 70px; height: 2px; background: #F5B700; }
        .section { padding: 80px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,183,0,0.1); }
        
        .btn-primary, .btn-outline, .portfolio-card, .hero-stats {
            background: rgba(18, 24, 32, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245,183,0,0.2);
            transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.9, 0.4, 1.1);
            border-top-left-radius: 28px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 28px;
            border-top-right-radius: 0;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 0;
        }
        .btn-primary, .btn-outline {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 12px 32px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: #F5B700;
            color: #0D1117;
            border: 1px solid #F5B700;
        }
        .btn-outline { background: transparent; color: #FFFFFF; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: transparent; color: #F5B700; }
        .btn-outline:hover { border-color: #F5B700; background: rgba(245,183,0,0.1); color: #F5B700; }
        
        .header { position: sticky; top: 0; background: rgba(13,17,23,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); z-index: 1000; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,183,0,0.2); padding: 18px 0; }
        .header .container { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .logo { font-family: 'Zen Dots', monospace; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .logo span:first-child { color: #F5B700; }
        .logo span:last-child { color: #FFFFFF; }
        .nav-menu { display: flex; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; }
        .nav-link { color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 400; transition: 0.2s; }
        .nav-link:hover { color: #F5B700; }
        .burger { display: none; flex-direction: column; cursor: pointer; gap: 6px; }
        .burger span { width: 28px; height: 2px; background: #F5B700; }
        .header-telegram {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #27A6E5;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }
        .header-telegram:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .header-telegram svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; fill: white; }
        
        .portfolio-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; margin-top: 40px; }
        .portfolio-card { padding: 0; overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer; }
        .portfolio-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); border-color: #F5B700; box-shadow: 0 20px 30px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .portfolio-image { height: 240px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1A212B, #0B1015); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 500; color: #F5B700; border-top-left-radius: 28px; }
        .portfolio-info { padding: 28px; }
        .portfolio-info h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #FFFFFF; }
        .portfolio-info p { color: #B0C4DE; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .portfolio-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
        .portfolio-tag { background: #11181F; padding: 4px 12px; font-size: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #2A3A44; border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; }
        
        .footer { background: #080C10; padding: 56px 0 32px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,183,0,0.15); margin-top: 40px; }
        .footer-grid { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 40px; }
        .footer-logo { color: #F5B700; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 500; font-family: 'Zen Dots', monospace; }
        .footer a { color: #B0C4DE; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.2s; }
        .footer a:hover { color: #F5B700; }
        .totop { position: fixed; bottom: 30px; right: 30px; background: #F5B700; width: 48px; height: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; border: none; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #0D1117; border-top-left-radius: 24px; border-bottom-right-radius: 24px; transition: 0.2s; z-index: 99; }
        .totop:hover { background: white; transform: translateY(-4px); }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container { padding: 0 24px; }
            h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .nav-menu { 
                position: fixed; 
                top: 70px; 
                right: -100%; 
                background: rgba(13,17,23,0.98); 
                backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
                flex-direction: column; 
                width: 70%; 
                height: 100vh; 
                padding: 30px; 
                transition: 0.3s; 
                border-left: 2px solid #F5B700; 
                z-index: 999; 
            }
            .nav-menu.active { right: 0; }
            .burger { display: flex; z-index: 1001; }
            .portfolio-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="header">
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="logo" aria-label="ALBE digital - главная"><span>a</span><span>lbe</span></a>
        <div class="burger" id="burgerBtn"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <nav class="nav-menu" id="navMenu">
            <a href="/" class="nav-link">Главная</a>
            <a href="/portfolio/" class="nav-link">Портфолио</a>
            <a href="/services/" class="nav-link">Услуги</a>
            <a href="/contacts/" class="nav-link">Контакты</a>
            <a href="tel:+79959870353" class="btn-outline" style="padding: 6px 20px;">+7 995 987 0353</a>
            <a href="https://t.me/albe_web" target="_blank" class="header-telegram" aria-label="Telegram">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm4.64 6.8c-.15 1.58-.8 5.42-1.13 7.19-.14.75-.42 1-.68 1.03-.58.05-1.02-.38-1.58-.75-.88-.6-1.38-.97-2.23-1.56-.99-.69-.35-1.07.22-1.69.15-.15 2.8-2.57 2.85-2.79.01-.06.02-.14-.05-.2-.07-.06-.18-.04-.26-.02-.12.03-1.97 1.25-5.57 3.68-.53.36-1.01.54-1.44.53-.47-.01-1.38-.27-2.06-.49-.84-.27-1.51-.42-1.45-.89.03-.25.37-.5 1.03-.76 4.04-1.76 6.73-2.92 8.09-3.48 3.85-1.59 4.65-1.86 5.17-1.87.12 0 .37.03.54.2.14.14.17.32.19.54-.04.18-.06.46-.09.78z" fill="white"/></svg>
            </a>
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>

<main>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Наши проекты</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #B0C4DE; max-width: 700px;">Реальные кейсы, которые демонстрируют наш подход, технологии и результаты.</p>
            
            <div class="portfolio-grid">
                <a href="/portfolio/neobank.html" class="portfolio-card" style="text-decoration: none; display: block;">
                    <div class="portfolio-image">NEO BANK</div>
                    <div class="portfolio-info">
                        <h3>NeoBank Platform</h3>
                        <p>Цифровой банк нового поколения с панелью аналитики и AI-рекомендациями.</p>
                        <div class="portfolio-tags">
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">Fintech</span>
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">React</span>
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">Node.js</span>
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">AI</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
                
                <a href="/portfolio/ai-recommend.html" class="portfolio-card" style="text-decoration: none; display: block;">
                    <div class="portfolio-image">AI RECOMMEND</div>
                    <div class="portfolio-info">
                        <h3>AI рекомендательная система</h3>
                        <p>Персональные рекомендации для e-commerce на основе машинного обучения.</p>
                        <div class="portfolio-tags">
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">E-commerce</span>
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">Python</span>
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">TensorFlow</span>
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">FastAPI</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
                
                <a href="/portfolio/fittrack.html" class="portfolio-card" style="text-decoration: none; display: block;">
                    <div class="portfolio-image">MOBILE APP</div>
                    <div class="portfolio-info">
                        <h3>FitTrack приложение</h3>
                        <p>Мобильное приложение для фитнес-студии с трекингом активности и онлайн-записью.</p>
                        <div class="portfolio-tags">
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">Mobile</span>
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">React Native</span>
                            <span class="portfolio-tag">Firebase</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="footer-grid">
            <div><div class="footer-logo">a<span style="color:#FFFFFF;">lbe</span></div><p style="margin-top: 12px;">Digital agency премиального уровня.</p></div>
            <div><h4 style="color:#F5B700;">Контакты</h4><p><a href="tel:+79959870353">+7 995 987 0353</a></p><p><a href="mailto:hello@albe.su">hello@albe.su</a></p><p><a href="https://t.me/albe_web" target="_blank">Telegram @albe_web</a></p></div>
            <div><h4 style="color:#F5B700;">Навигация</h4><p><a href="/">Главная</a></p><p><a href="/portfolio/">Портфолио</a></p><p><a href="/services/">Услуги</a></p><p><a href="/contacts/">Контакты</a></p></div>
        </div>
        <hr style="border-color:#1E2A32; margin: 32px 0 20px;">
        <p style="text-align: center;">© 2025 ALBE digital — разработка сайтов, дизайн, AI, SEO. <a href="/privacy/">Политика конфиденциальности</a></p>
    </div>
</footer>
<div class="totop" id="toTopBtn">↑</div>

<script>
    const burger = document.getElementById('burgerBtn');
    const navMenu = document.getElementById('navMenu');
    if(burger) burger.addEventListener('click', () => navMenu.classList.toggle('active'));
    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-link').forEach(l => l.addEventListener('click', () => navMenu.classList.remove('active')));
    
    const toTop = document.getElementById('toTopBtn');
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => { if(toTop) toTop.style.display = window.scrollY > 400 ? 'flex' : 'none'; });
    if(toTop) { toTop.style.display = 'none'; toTop.addEventListener('click', () => window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' })); }
</script>
</body>
</html>
